'''Shah Rukh Khan''' ({{IPA-hns|ˈʃɑːɦɾʊx xɑːn|pron}}; 2 Nofeembar 1965), sidoo kale loo yaqaan bilawga '''SRK''', waa atoore Hindi ah, filim soo saare, iyo shaqsi telefishin ah oo ka shaqeeya [[Bollywood|filimada Hindiga]]. Waxaa loogu yeeraa warbaahinta inuu yahay "'''Baadshah of Bollywood'''" (iyadoo loo tixraacayo filimkiisii 1999 ee ''[[Baadshah]]''), "Boqorka Bollywoodka" iyo "King Khan", wuxuu kasoo muuqday in ka badan 80 filim, wuxuuna helay abaal-marinno badan, oo ay ku jiraan 14 [[abaalmarinta Filmfare]]. [[Dowlada Hindiya]] ayaa ku abaal marisay [[Padma Shri]], waxaana [[dowlada Faransiiska]] ay gudoonsiisay abaal marinta [[Ordre des Arts et des Lettres]] iyo [[Guutada Sharafta]]. Khan ayaa taageere weyn ku leh Aasiya iyo [[Aan deganayn Hindida iyo Muwaadin Dibadeed ee Hindiya|qurba-joogta Hindiya]] ee adduunka oo dhan. Marka la eego tirada daawadayaasha iyo dakhliga soo gala, waxaa lagu tilmaamaa inuu yahay mid ka mid ah jilayaasha filimada ugu guulaha badan adduunka.

Khan waxa uu shaqadiisa ku bilaabay muuqaalo dhowr ah oo taxane telefishin ah dhamaadkii 1980-meeyadii. Filimkii ugu horeeyay ee uu keeno Bollywoodka waxa uu ahaa ''[[Deewana]]'' sanadii 1992-kii. Horaantii xirfadiisa Khan waxaa loo aqoonsaday inuu ku matalo doorar xunxun ee filimada ''[[Baazigar]]'' (1993), ''[[Darr]]'' (1993), iyo ''[[Anjaam]]'' (1994). Ka dib waxa uu soo shaac baxay ka dib markii uu jilay filimo jacayl ah oo ay ka mid yihiin ''[[Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge]]'' (1995), ''[[Dil To Pagal Hai]]'' (1997), ''[[Kuch Kuch Hota Hai]]'' (1998), ''[[Mohabbatein]]'' (2000) iyo ''[[Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham...]]'' (2001). Khan wuxuu sii waday inuu ku kasbado amaan muhiim ah doorkisa khamriga ee ''[[Devdas]]'' (2002), saynisyahan [[NASA]] ah ee ''[[Swades]]'' (2004), tababare xeegada ''[[Chak De! India]]'' (2007) iyo nin qaba [[Cilladda asperger]] ee ''[[My Name Is Khan]]'' (2010). Aflaantiisa lacagaha ugu badan soo xareeyay waxaa ka mid ah ''[[Chennai Express]]'' (2013), ''[[Happy New Year (filim)|Happy New Year]]'' (2014), ''[[Dilwale]]'' (2015), iyo ''[[Raees]]'' (2017).  Qaar badan oo filimadiisa ka mid ah waxay soo bandhigaan mawduucyo aqoonsi qaran Hindi ah iyo xidhiidhka bulshooyinka qurbaha, ama jinsiga, jinsiyadda, bulshada iyo diinta kala duwanaanshaha iyo cabashooyinka.

Laga bilaabo 2015, Khan waa la-guddoomiyaha shirkadda wax soo saarka [[Red Chillies Entertainment]]  waana la-milkiilaha kooxda [[Horyaalka Hindiya]] ee [[Kolkata Knight Riders]] iyo kooxda [[Horyaalka Kaaribiyaan]]-ka [[Trinbago Knight Riders]]. Dadaalka kheyriga ah ee Khan ayaa bixiyay daryeel caafimaad iyo gargaar musiibo, waxaana lagu sharfay abaalmarinta [[UNESCO]] ee 2011 taageerada uu u fidiyay waxbarashada carruurta iyo Abaalmarinta Crystal ee [[Madasha Dhaqaalaha Adduunka]] ee 2018 oo uu ku muteystay hoggaankiisa u ololeynta xuquuqda haweenka iyo carruurta ee Hindiya.

